```{r setup, include=FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
library(tibble)
library(skimr)
library(magrittr)
library(purrr)
library(ggtext)
library(grid)
library(ggrepel)
library(directlabels)
library(reshape2)

```

```{r loadingData, echo=FALSE}

resq_anon <- read_csv("resq-raw-data/anon_data_Hendrik.csv")

resq_clean <- na.omit(resq_anon)

resq_df<-resq_clean %>%
  group_by(hospital, year) %>%
  summarise(
    DTNMedian=median(DTN),
    DTNMean=mean(DTN),
    AgeMean=mean(age)
    )

#resq_df$DTNMedian<250 &  
ggplot(resq_df[resq_df$DTNMean < 200 & resq_df$year>=2016,], aes(x = year, y = DTNMean)) + 
  geom_line(aes(color = factor(hospital)), show.legend = FALSE) + geom_smooth()

```
